    "iast": "sarva-dvārāṇi saṃyamya mano hṛdi nirudhya ca | mūrdhny ādhāyātmanaḥ prāṇam āsthito yoga-dhāraṇām",
    "chapter_position": "Chapter 8 (Akṣara-Brahma-Yoga (The Yoga of the Imperishable Brahman)), verse 12",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "addressed_to": "Arjuna"
